            <div type="a">
                <column>02</column>
                <head>Death of a Physician</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names>
                    <name>
                        <ln>McGovran</ln>
                        <fn>Edmund G.</fn>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf>Dr.</pf>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Dr. Edmund G. McGovran died in his residence in Chambersburg. He was buried
                    in the Catholic cemetery. He had practiced for many years in Loudon,
                    Mercersburg, Cumberland County, and Virginia. "He was held in high esteem by all
                    who knew him for his gentlemanly qualities and professional skill."</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
